Q: James loved to surf but he wasn't good at it. He would always do what?
greedyA:
A

Since James wasn't good at surfing, he would likely experience a lot of falls or crashes in the water, which is commonly referred to as "wiping out." This is a common experience for beginners or inexperienced surfers.
